// Create a .vimrc file in your /home directory
$ sudo vim .vimrc

// Set your default rules
se nu
set wrapmargin=4
set ruler

// Save the file inside vim editor
// Press Esc + :wq

// Or if you didn't name the file yet
// Press Esc + :w .vimrc (if you are in /home directory)
// Press Esc + :w ~/.vimrc (if you are not in /home)
